15
00:02:11,340 --> 00:02:13,260
=Episode 02=

16
00:02:19,760 --> 00:02:23,080
Long live the Empress.

17
00:02:24,190 --> 00:02:24,880
Rise.

18
00:02:45,960 --> 00:02:47,800
(She looks just like me.)

19
00:02:50,240 --> 00:02:52,000
(No one finds it weird?)

20
00:02:53,030 --> 00:02:53,880
(Well, they do say that)

21
00:02:54,440 --> 00:02:56,000
(nieces tend to look like their aunts.)

22
00:02:57,670 --> 00:02:59,240
(He must be surprised too.)

23
00:03:00,600 --> 00:03:02,000
(That's Cheng Cheng.)

24
00:03:08,440 --> 00:03:09,390
Oh, no.

25
00:03:11,750 --> 00:03:13,470
(Why are you so excited seeing Cheng Cheng?)

26
00:03:16,030 --> 00:03:17,360
(Cheng Cheng is mine.)

27
00:03:18,600 --> 00:03:21,910
Now, the people live in peace

28
00:03:22,520 --> 00:03:24,080
and the nation is united.

29
00:03:25,160 --> 00:03:27,240
But I couldn't slack off.

30
00:03:27,800 --> 00:03:30,550
So I select harem candidates
once every three years.

31
00:03:31,470 --> 00:03:33,390
Is there anyone who can alleviate my concerns?

32
00:03:35,630 --> 00:03:36,720
Your Majesty,

33
00:03:37,360 --> 00:03:40,200
The Eighth Young Master of
the Mo family is versatile。

34
00:03:40,960 --> 00:03:42,190
He's the most outstanding candidate.

35
00:03:49,880 --> 00:03:50,910
Your Majesty,

36
00:03:51,670 --> 00:03:54,720
I find Young Master Mo quite reserved.

37
00:03:55,000 --> 00:03:55,910
He is a boring person.

38
00:03:56,030 --> 00:03:59,110
I'm afraid he does not possess the talent
to entertain you, Your Majesty.

39
00:03:59,830 --> 00:04:03,160
Young Master Mo has excellent sword skills.

40
00:04:03,750 --> 00:04:06,080
Then why don't we have him
perform for us right now?

41
00:04:06,520 --> 00:04:09,760
He'll be able to convince the other
candidates of his skills as well.

42
00:04:12,080 --> 00:04:13,800
Your Majesty. Princess.

43
00:04:14,670 --> 00:04:16,320
It is inappropriate to brandish
a sword in the great hall.

44
00:04:16,550 --> 00:04:17,270
I'm afraid...

45
00:04:17,270 --> 00:04:18,080
It doesn't matter.

46
00:04:24,550 --> 00:04:25,320
Yes, Your Majesty.

47
00:05:31,950 --> 00:05:33,510
Isn't this my perfume sachet?

48
00:05:33,920 --> 00:05:35,160
Why is it with you?

49
00:05:37,160 --> 00:05:40,160
Your Majesty, Mo Lian Cheng is concealing
a woman's personal belonging.

50
00:05:40,200 --> 00:05:41,200
His actions are improper.

51
00:05:41,350 --> 00:05:42,480
He has been caught red-handed.

52
00:05:42,760 --> 00:05:44,270
Please deal with him accordingly.

53
00:05:47,030 --> 00:05:49,390
Mo Lian Cheng, what is going on with you?

54
00:05:57,510 --> 00:05:58,550
Your Majesty, please review it carefully.

55
00:05:59,010 --> 00:06:00,210
We should be asking when did the owner

56
00:06:00,230 --> 00:06:01,230
of the perfume sachet remove it

57
00:06:01,440 --> 00:06:03,160
and when did the attendant responsible
for her attire put it back in place.

58
00:06:03,670 --> 00:06:06,920
Only I, who have had my body searched,
should not be asked such a question.

59
00:06:09,200 --> 00:06:09,950
Your Majesty,

60
00:06:10,440 --> 00:06:11,790
there should be no problems

61
00:06:11,950 --> 00:06:13,390
with clothes prepared in the palace.

62
00:06:14,350 --> 00:06:15,720
I would not have come into contact

63
00:06:16,320 --> 00:06:18,040
Her Highness' perfume sachet either.

64
00:06:20,070 --> 00:06:22,110
You spilled tea on me on purpose.

65
00:06:22,160 --> 00:06:24,200
You must have done it because you admire me

66
00:06:24,600 --> 00:06:26,350
and took the sachet when I was changing my clothes.

67
00:06:28,320 --> 00:06:29,670
Your Highness knows very well

68
00:06:30,000 --> 00:06:31,480
how the tea was split and who

69
00:06:31,790 --> 00:06:33,110
requested a change of clothes.

70
00:06:35,480 --> 00:06:36,480
Your Majesty,

71
00:06:36,600 --> 00:06:38,600
there are a lot of doubts regarding today's matter.

72
00:06:38,880 --> 00:06:41,320
If word got out, it might do the harem harm.

73
00:06:41,480 --> 00:06:42,670
Even if Young Master Mo was wronged,

74
00:06:42,670 --> 00:06:44,070
everything that has happened today

75
00:06:44,200 --> 00:06:46,110
proves that he is unfit to participate
in the harem selection.

76
00:06:46,480 --> 00:06:49,270
Your Majesty, please remove him from the list.

77
00:06:50,480 --> 00:06:51,920
Things haven't come out in the wash.

78
00:06:52,600 --> 00:06:55,040
Why does Your Highness refuse to
allow me to defend myself?

79
00:06:55,760 --> 00:06:56,390
Ultimately,

80
00:06:56,480 --> 00:06:58,390
that perfume sachet fell out of your sleeves.

81
00:06:58,440 --> 00:06:59,760
Everyone here saw that.

82
00:07:00,230 --> 00:07:01,110
Or do you wish

83
00:07:01,320 --> 00:07:03,390
that Her Majesty be criticized by people?

84
00:07:03,600 --> 00:07:04,040
You...

85
00:07:05,110 --> 00:07:06,160
Official Su.

86
00:07:08,070 --> 00:07:09,480
Investigate this matter.

87
00:07:10,920 --> 00:07:11,720
Yes, Your Majesty.

88
00:07:12,110 --> 00:07:13,110
Your Majesty is wise.

89
00:07:27,220 --> 00:07:29,780
(Mo Residence)

90
00:07:41,600 --> 00:07:44,270
For generations, the Mo family
has always been revered.

91
00:07:44,600 --> 00:07:46,230
Yet today, you have tarnished our reputation.

92
00:07:47,390 --> 00:07:49,510
Not only have we become the laughing
stock of the residence,

93
00:07:49,720 --> 00:07:51,160
even the government officials
in the neighborhood

94
00:07:51,200 --> 00:07:52,670
have a lot to say about you!

95
00:07:53,160 --> 00:07:54,600
What do you think we should do?

96
00:07:55,000 --> 00:07:57,640
Father, Eighth Brother has always been
a man with good character.

97
00:07:57,790 --> 00:07:58,720
It must be a misunderstanding

98
00:07:58,920 --> 00:08:00,000
regarding today's matter.

99
00:08:00,720 --> 00:08:03,720
Her Majesty has ordered someone
to investigate it, hasn't she?

100
00:08:04,110 --> 00:08:06,320
I'm sure the truth will come out soon.

101
00:08:06,480 --> 00:08:07,230
Eldest Brother is right.

102
00:08:07,670 --> 00:08:08,640
Once the truth is out,

103
00:08:08,920 --> 00:08:10,390
we'll see if those slanderers

104
00:08:10,510 --> 00:08:11,270
will be ashamed or not.

105
00:08:11,320 --> 00:08:12,790
What do you know, Fourteenth?

106
00:08:13,270 --> 00:08:14,160
Shut up!

107
00:08:14,670 --> 00:08:16,110
I was asking him. Not you!

108
00:08:18,350 --> 00:08:20,950
People only wish to believe
what they want to believe.

109
00:08:21,110 --> 00:08:22,070
And they enjoy it.

110
00:08:22,600 --> 00:08:23,510
The only thing we can do

111
00:08:23,720 --> 00:08:25,270
is break the rumors by revealing the truth.

112
00:08:25,270 --> 00:08:26,640
The Mo family has already been
criticized by people.

113
00:08:26,830 --> 00:08:27,950
Does the truth still matter?

114
00:08:29,350 --> 00:08:30,720
You don't get to decide if you were right or wrong.

115
00:08:30,720 --> 00:08:31,920
Her Majesty decides that.

116
00:08:32,270 --> 00:08:33,830
Before Her Majesty decides what to do with you,

117
00:08:34,160 --> 00:08:35,200
you will copy the moral codes for men every day.

118
00:08:35,270 --> 00:08:36,070
You will do that right now!

119
00:08:39,760 --> 00:08:40,440
Yes, Father.

120
00:08:45,840 --> 00:08:46,590
Eighth Brother.

121
00:08:58,230 --> 00:09:00,440
You are saying that he stole your perfume sachet?

122
00:09:02,350 --> 00:09:04,400
Could it be because you and Her Majesty

123
00:09:04,400 --> 00:09:06,080
look alike, he has fallen

124
00:09:06,230 --> 00:09:07,590
for you instead?

125
00:09:11,280 --> 00:09:12,280
But that's not right.

126
00:09:12,960 --> 00:09:15,000
If he didn't do something so foolish,

127
00:09:15,350 --> 00:09:17,030
he'd have successfully joined the harem.

128
00:09:17,440 --> 00:09:18,520
Why would he even need to shift
his attention to another person?

129
00:09:19,080 --> 00:09:20,880
(The entire world knows)

130
00:09:21,230 --> 00:09:22,760
(that I look like Her Majesty.)

131
00:09:23,350 --> 00:09:24,280
(I guess I'll have to pretend)

132
00:09:24,550 --> 00:09:26,590
(that I'm used to it as well.)

133
00:09:33,960 --> 00:09:34,710
Your Highness?

134
00:09:39,880 --> 00:09:42,320
He was framed.

135
00:09:42,670 --> 00:09:43,640
I just

136
00:09:43,840 --> 00:09:46,000
gave them an extra push.

137
00:09:46,080 --> 00:09:47,030
Why?

138
00:09:50,000 --> 00:09:52,280
Maybe you guys are thinking
in the wrong direction?

139
00:09:52,880 --> 00:09:54,320
Have you guys never thought

140
00:09:54,550 --> 00:09:56,440
that the reason this kind of thing has happened

141
00:09:57,080 --> 00:09:59,280
was that Her Majesty looks like me?

142
00:10:00,840 --> 00:10:02,710
You mustn't say that, Your Highness!

143
00:10:02,910 --> 00:10:04,400
That is highly disrespectful.

144
00:10:04,840 --> 00:10:06,880
Aren't you a brave and invincible guard?

145
00:10:06,960 --> 00:10:08,280
Why are you such a coward?

146
00:10:09,280 --> 00:10:10,880
Stopping Your Highness from getting
into trouble due to your loose tongue

147
00:10:11,110 --> 00:10:13,150
is also part of my duties as
protecting Your Highness.

148
00:10:15,840 --> 00:10:20,150
However... Regardless of what happened
between Her Majesty and him,

149
00:10:20,440 --> 00:10:22,320
I only had to use a little trick

150
00:10:22,320 --> 00:10:24,150
to make him pliant.

151
00:10:25,200 --> 00:10:27,470
Let's see if he dares to look down on me again.

152
00:10:27,640 --> 00:10:29,320
Your Highness's plan was flawless.

153
00:10:29,910 --> 00:10:31,320
However, with your interference,

154
00:10:31,840 --> 00:10:34,670
I'm afraid Eighth Young Master will no longer
be able to have a good marriage.

155
00:10:35,000 --> 00:10:37,710
The entire Mo family will be affected as well.

156
00:10:39,350 --> 00:10:41,080
Are things really as serious as you say?

157
00:10:41,400 --> 00:10:42,230
Think about it.

158
00:10:42,790 --> 00:10:44,110
Men's futures

159
00:10:44,110 --> 00:10:46,200
have everything to do with their reputation.

160
00:10:46,350 --> 00:10:48,910
If a man's reputation is tarnished,

161
00:10:49,000 --> 00:10:50,640
that'll be the end of their futures as well.

162
00:10:51,000 --> 00:10:53,520
The reputation of the Mo family will also...

163
00:10:54,670 --> 00:10:57,000
Are you saying that he might
be kicked out of his house?

164
00:10:57,030 --> 00:10:58,440
I'm afraid not only that.

165
00:10:58,590 --> 00:10:59,960
Her Majesty is involved.

166
00:11:00,280 --> 00:11:01,710
If he is found guilty,

167
00:11:02,030 --> 00:11:03,280
a lighter sentence would mean that
he'll be sent to become a monk.

168
00:11:03,550 --> 00:11:05,880
A heavier sentence might mean
he'll be dipped in a pig cage.

169
00:11:06,200 --> 00:11:07,400
Dipped in a pig cage?

170
00:11:09,880 --> 00:11:12,520
Oh, no. Things got out of hand this time.

171
00:11:13,230 --> 00:11:15,030
His brothers

172
00:11:15,200 --> 00:11:16,550
may be affected as well.

173
00:11:17,520 --> 00:11:18,400
Jing Xin.

174
00:11:18,670 --> 00:11:20,230
Come with me to the Mo Residence. Hurry!

175
00:11:31,080 --> 00:11:32,080
Are we almost there yet?

176
00:11:33,280 --> 00:11:35,320
The Mo Residence is up ahead, Your Highness.

177
00:11:36,910 --> 00:11:38,200
A cherry blossom tree?

178
00:11:39,520 --> 00:11:40,320
Quick, stop the carriage.

179
00:11:40,320 --> 00:11:41,230
But we're not there yet.

180
00:11:41,550 --> 00:11:42,280
Stop the carriage!

181
00:11:42,440 --> 00:11:43,030
Stop the carriage!

182
00:11:44,320 --> 00:11:44,960
Your Highness!

183
00:11:52,350 --> 00:11:53,110
Your Highness,

184
00:11:53,110 --> 00:11:54,200
I'll go and notify them first.

185
00:11:56,150 --> 00:11:57,520
Please wait here.

186
00:12:01,350 --> 00:12:04,790
It really is the tree... It must be fate.

187
00:12:06,110 --> 00:12:07,640
No matter how many times I come here,

188
00:12:07,960 --> 00:12:10,960
the person I love is waiting for me
on the other side of the wall.

189
00:12:33,960 --> 00:12:35,960
How come I awfully succeeded this time?

190
00:12:40,000 --> 00:12:42,110
Oh, it's because Jing Xin isn't here.

191
00:12:43,640 --> 00:12:44,550
Where is Jing Xin?

192
00:12:45,150 --> 00:12:47,150
Jing Xin? Jing Xin!

193
00:12:50,280 --> 00:12:52,670
Never mind. Forget about her.

194
00:12:52,670 --> 00:12:54,000
I'll just climb in by myself.

195
00:12:54,880 --> 00:12:57,280
This body... This process...

196
00:12:57,880 --> 00:12:59,640
This body is too used to this.

197
00:13:04,790 --> 00:13:07,590
Cheng Cheng! Cheng Cheng!

198
00:13:08,350 --> 00:13:10,440
Cheng Cheng, it's me!

199
00:13:11,520 --> 00:13:13,440
Come and catch me!

200
00:13:28,110 --> 00:13:31,110
He is doing better this time.

201
00:13:40,790 --> 00:13:42,320
I've lost all my limberness

202
00:13:42,790 --> 00:13:45,000
from taking care of the kids for all these years.

203
00:13:47,440 --> 00:13:50,200
I'm going down now, Cheng Cheng.

204
00:13:50,520 --> 00:13:51,640
You have to catch me.

205
00:13:51,790 --> 00:13:52,440
Here I come.

206
00:13:56,590 --> 00:13:57,880
Catch me!

207
00:13:57,900 --> 00:14:01,780
♪The most beautiful moment
is when I fell for you♪

208
00:14:01,860 --> 00:14:05,340
♪Infatuation leads me to jump into a vortex♪

209
00:14:05,700 --> 00:14:10,140
♪From breaking down the barriers
to falling helplessly in love♪

210
00:14:10,980 --> 00:14:15,500
♪Every step is a desperate struggle♪

211
00:14:16,860 --> 00:14:20,780
♪An opened heart, a mistake made♪

212
00:14:21,670 --> 00:14:22,960
Mo Lian Cheng!

213
00:14:30,230 --> 00:14:32,840
You let me fall right in front of you again.

214
00:14:32,960 --> 00:14:34,320
You do that every single time!

215
00:14:35,030 --> 00:14:36,110
It hurts a lot.

216
00:14:36,710 --> 00:14:37,350
Men and women...

217
00:14:37,400 --> 00:14:38,710
Should have no direct contact.

218
00:14:39,020 --> 00:14:43,140
♪To love till the world turns upside down,
all for this moment of happiness♪

219
00:14:44,280 --> 00:14:44,910
Tan Er.

220
00:14:46,760 --> 00:14:47,760
(Who is that?)

221
00:14:48,030 --> 00:14:49,960
(He even calls me Tan Er.)

222
00:14:51,080 --> 00:14:52,550
(I've never seen him before.)

223
00:14:53,440 --> 00:14:54,400
(He is quite handsome though.)

224
00:14:55,640 --> 00:14:56,790
Yan Chen came late.

225
00:14:58,280 --> 00:14:59,150
You're not hurt, are you?

226
00:14:59,280 --> 00:15:01,150
Here, let me see if you were injured.

227
00:15:01,350 --> 00:15:02,440
I'm fine.

228
00:15:06,000 --> 00:15:06,880
Don't worry.

229
00:15:07,030 --> 00:15:08,790
Eighth Brother knows about
our feelings for each other.

230
00:15:10,350 --> 00:15:11,230
(Feelings?)

231
00:15:11,400 --> 00:15:12,520
(Shouldn't Qu Tan Er and Mo Yi Huai)

232
00:15:12,520 --> 00:15:14,230
(be the ones who have feelings for each other?)

233
00:15:14,670 --> 00:15:17,350
(This guy said his name is Yan Chen.)

234
00:15:17,840 --> 00:15:21,000
(Mo Yan Chen... Then what about Mo Yi Huai?)

235
00:15:22,000 --> 00:15:24,000
(This is confusing.)

236
00:15:24,670 --> 00:15:25,350
Tan Er?

237
00:15:26,760 --> 00:15:28,030
You're mistaken.

238
00:15:28,280 --> 00:15:30,280
I came because of...

239
00:15:31,350 --> 00:15:32,110
Of course I know that

240
00:15:32,110 --> 00:15:33,550
the matter with Eighth Brother
was all a misunderstanding.

241
00:15:33,590 --> 00:15:35,230
And you came to resolve it.

242
00:15:35,280 --> 00:15:37,760
Come with me to see my father in the main hall.

243
00:15:50,520 --> 00:15:51,640
Where is Her Highness?

244
00:15:59,520 --> 00:16:00,200
Please.

245
00:16:05,880 --> 00:16:06,910
Please wait for a moment.

246
00:16:12,280 --> 00:16:12,910
Your Highness.

247
00:16:13,230 --> 00:16:13,790
Jing Xin.

248
00:16:13,790 --> 00:16:15,080
Where were you earlier?

249
00:16:19,080 --> 00:16:20,110
We'll talk later.

250
00:16:30,550 --> 00:16:31,470
Father.

251
00:16:32,640 --> 00:16:33,880
Greetings, Your Highness.

252
00:16:34,000 --> 00:16:35,320
Your Highness has come to our humble abode.

253
00:16:35,320 --> 00:16:36,280
Yet I did not greet you at the entrance.

254
00:16:36,350 --> 00:16:37,790
Please forgive me, Your Highness.

255
00:16:38,710 --> 00:16:40,230
Father...

256
00:16:42,880 --> 00:16:44,150
(I almost forgot.)

257
00:16:44,320 --> 00:16:46,030
(He is no longer the emperor.)

258
00:16:46,320 --> 00:16:48,350
(There are so many things I have to get used to.)

259
00:16:50,670 --> 00:16:51,550
Mr. Mo.

260
00:16:53,230 --> 00:16:54,080
Senior.

261
00:16:58,880 --> 00:17:00,030
Mr. Mo.

262
00:17:04,200 --> 00:17:05,400
I came here today

263
00:17:05,960 --> 00:17:09,520
specifically for Eighth Young Master's candidacy.

264
00:17:09,840 --> 00:17:11,280
It was all a misunderstanding.

265
00:17:11,910 --> 00:17:13,110
It wasn't my intention to cause

266
00:17:13,590 --> 00:17:14,790
so much trouble for the Mo family.

267
00:17:15,110 --> 00:17:16,310
Your Highness' misunderstanding

268
00:17:16,470 --> 00:17:18,070
did make our family

269
00:17:18,160 --> 00:17:19,710
get into trouble.

270
00:17:20,470 --> 00:17:22,400
I especially came here today to tell you

271
00:17:22,640 --> 00:17:24,280
