you then, Your Highness.

286
00:18:02,620 --> 00:18:06,500
(Mo Residence)

287
00:18:08,070 --> 00:18:10,160
I haven't figured out what happened
to Cheng Cheng yet.

288
00:18:10,520 --> 00:18:11,590
I can't go back to Dongyue.

289
00:18:11,760 --> 00:18:13,190
And I can't see my Yu Er.

290
00:18:13,950 --> 00:18:16,070
And there's this mess right now.

291
00:18:20,710 --> 00:18:23,710
