Cheng Cheng's reputation?

292
00:18:27,800 --> 00:18:28,680
Jing Xin.

293
00:18:29,230 --> 00:18:30,000
Let me ask you.

294
00:18:30,190 --> 00:18:32,350
Is there a way to spread one's good deeds

295
00:18:32,640 --> 00:18:34,830
around fast

296
00:18:34,830 --> 00:18:35,950
