297
00:18:36,800 --> 00:18:39,560
You could find a storyteller.

298
00:18:42,470 --> 00:18:43,230
That's right.

299
00:18:45,760 --> 00:18:49,430
I'll have him write a story on Mo Lian Cheng.

300
00:18:49,560 --> 00:18:50,760
And

301
00:18:50,920 --> 00:18:53,350
we'll get the most famous and popular storyteller

302
00:18:53,640 --> 00:18:55,680
