303
00:18:56,680 --> 00:18:57,880
Get it done right now.

304
00:18:57,950 --> 00:18:59,750
The story must be delivered tomorrow.

305
00:19:00,350 --> 00:19:02,280
Yes, Your Highness. I'll get to it right away.

306
00:19:02,950 --> 00:19:03,680
Wait.

307
00:19:05,400 --> 00:19:07,160
That doesn't seem enough.

308
00:19:08,230 --> 00:19:09,310
Find a mason.

309
00:19:09,640 --> 00:19:11,710
One that's good at carving scripts.

310
00:19:12,070 --> 00:19:14,160
And find a few kids

311
00:19:14,160 --> 00:19:16,520
that are smart and good with words.

312
00:19:17,070 --> 00:19:18,430
We'll turn it into a nursery rhyme

313
00:19:18,590 --> 00:19:20,230
and have the children sing it all across the city!

314
00:19:21,280 --> 00:19:22,000
That should do it.

315
00:19:22,560 --> 00:19:23,310
Go on now.

316
00:19:24,640 --> 00:19:25,160
Yes, Your Highness.

317
00:19:40,830 --> 00:19:41,520
Her Majesty wants to know the results

318
00:19:41,520 --> 00:19:43,760
of the investigation regarding
the harem candidate incident.

319
00:19:43,880 --> 00:19:46,160
That is why she has asked both of you to come here today.

320
00:19:46,640 --> 00:19:48,430
So you can give Her Highness an explanation as well.

321
00:19:48,800 --> 00:19:50,640
But why has Official Su

322
00:19:50,640 --> 00:19:52,430
yet to report to Her Majesty?

323
00:19:54,280 --> 00:19:55,760
I have failed my duties.

324
00:19:55,950 --> 00:19:58,230
Please ask Her Majesty to allow
a few extra days of grace.

325
00:19:58,430 --> 00:19:59,920
I will do my best to ensure that

326
00:20:00,070 --> 00:20:02,920
I find the evidence that proves that
Young Master Mo was framed.

327
00:20:03,230 --> 00:20:05,880
Her Majesty asked you to find the truth.

328
00:20:09,160 --> 00:20:10,640
I know the truth.

329
00:20:12,190 --> 00:20:13,470
Did Your Highness

330
00:20:13,590 --> 00:20:14,560
find evidence that proves

331
00:20:14,560 --> 00:20:16,310
Eighth Young Master stole your perfume sachet?

332
00:20:17,070 --> 00:20:18,880
The truth is...

333
00:20:21,110 --> 00:20:22,640
Mo Lian Cheng...

334
00:20:25,000 --> 00:20:26,520
was framed.

335
00:20:26,830 --> 00:20:28,040
But on the day of the harem selection,

336
00:20:28,190 --> 00:20:31,280
Your Highness was the one who insisted
that it was Mo Lian Cheng who stole it.

337
00:20:32,310 --> 00:20:33,190
I saw

338
00:20:33,230 --> 00:20:35,470
