339
00:20:35,560 --> 00:20:37,350
I was blinded by a moment of rage.

340
00:20:37,430 --> 00:20:39,710
When I thought about it again,

341
00:20:40,000 --> 00:20:43,040
I realized that everyone in Dongyue

342
