350
00:21:06,110 --> 00:21:07,430
If you wish to find out

351
00:21:07,520 --> 00:21:09,950
if Young Master Mo was framed by someone,

352
00:21:11,920 --> 00:21:13,800
or by whom,

353
00:21:14,430 --> 00:21:15,190
you only need to...

354
00:21:17,280 --> 00:21:18,640
gather

355
00:21:18,640 --> 00:21:19,640
the harem candidates

356
00:21:20,190 --> 00:21:21,310
and release the butterflies.

357
00:21:22,160 --> 00:21:23,190
Apart from

358
00:21:23,310 --> 00:21:25,400
Mo Lian Cheng and I, the butterflies

359
00:21:26,310 --> 00:21:27,680
would land on...

360
00:21:28,680 --> 00:21:32,280
of course the most suspicious

361
00:21:36,560 --> 00:21:38,040
harem candidates.

362
00:21:43,040 --> 00:21:44,350
In order to find out the truth,

363
00:21:44,640 --> 00:21:47,110
this is an experiment worth testing.

364
00:21:47,110 --> 00:21:48,000
There is no need for that!

365
00:21:50,830 --> 00:21:53,470
This... This isn't necessary.

366
00:21:54,040 --> 00:21:57,400
