369
00:22:07,400 --> 00:22:09,520
The Mo family are descendants
of the nation's founding members.

370
00:22:09,800 --> 00:22:12,950
I'm sure Her Majesty will be pleased to know
that Eighth Young Master's reputation

371
00:22:13,230 --> 00:22:14,880
has been rebuilt.

372
00:22:16,190 --> 00:22:18,590
I will report this matter to Her Majesty.

373
00:22:20,430 --> 00:22:21,800
I was incompetent.

374
00:22:22,470 --> 00:22:25,470
Her Highness was observant.

375
00:22:25,830 --> 00:22:27,830
I am ashamed.

376
00:22:31,520 --> 00:22:33,560
I've always known

377
00:22:34,230 --> 00:22:38,680
that Official Su is loyal to Her Majesty.

378
00:22:38,880 --> 00:22:42,000
However, if someone around Her Majesty

379
00:22:44,880 --> 00:22:48,710
