380
00:22:49,190 --> 00:22:51,640
That is a matter that must not be taken lightly.

381
00:22:51,710 --> 00:22:52,760
Yes, yes.

382
00:22:53,190 --> 00:22:54,920
Your Highness is right.

383
00:23:03,800 --> 00:23:06,920
I shall take my leave then.

384
00:23:15,590 --> 00:23:17,520
Your Majesty, as per your orders,

385
00:23:17,640 --> 00:23:19,040
I have summoned both of them to the palace.

386
00:23:19,350 --> 00:23:20,680
I have verified the matter.

387
00:23:20,920 --> 00:23:24,710
Su Yue La's brother, Su Jing Yuan,
has been suspected of framing Mo Lian Cheng.

388
00:23:28,760 --> 00:23:30,230
Leave Su Yue La.

389
00:23:30,400 --> 00:23:31,880
I still have use for her.

390
00:23:32,160 --> 00:23:33,760
As for her brother...

391
00:23:34,350 --> 00:23:35,800
Punish him according to the laws.

392
00:23:39,880 --> 00:23:42,680
Do you also think that Qu Tan Er
spoke up for Mo Lian Cheng

393
00:23:42,920 --> 00:23:44,000
during the harem selection

394
00:23:44,000 --> 00:23:45,640
to earn my favor?

395
00:23:46,710 --> 00:23:50,190
I suppose it may have just
been a misunderstanding

396
00:23:50,800 --> 00:23:52,190
when she accused Mo Lian Cheng.

397
00:23:52,680 --> 00:23:54,110
After all, she has always been

398
00:23:54,350 --> 00:23:56,040
respectful to Your Majesty.

399
00:24:07,920 --> 00:24:08,430
Cheng...

400
00:24:11,230 --> 00:24:12,040
Oh, you're all here.

401
00:24:12,640 --> 00:24:13,680
Perfect.

402
00:24:14,590 --> 00:24:15,560
Your Highness.

403
00:24:19,950 --> 00:24:20,710
How do you think?

404
00:24:21,110 --> 00:24:22,400
Not only did I

405
00:24:22,400 --> 00:24:23,950
clear your name in the palace,

406
00:24:24,070 --> 00:24:25,070
but I also

407
00:24:25,070 --> 00:24:26,920
rebuilt your reputation in the streets as well.

408
00:24:27,280 --> 00:24:29,310
Are you surprised?

409
00:24:29,830 --> 00:24:31,760
Think about how you're going to thank me.

410
00:24:32,190 --> 00:24:33,950
Your Highness is indeed considerate.

411
00:24:34,190 --> 00:24:35,680
I'm sure

412
00:24:35,920 --> 00:24:37,160
that everyone in Dongyue

413
00:24:37,190 --> 00:24:39,190
