414
00:24:39,230 --> 00:24:40,230
What do you mean?

415
00:24:41,000 --> 00:24:42,760
What's with that tone?

416
00:24:43,590 --> 00:24:44,400
Tan Er.

417
00:24:45,230 --> 00:24:46,880
The storyteller in the tea houses.

418
00:24:47,070 --> 00:24:48,520
The nursery rhymes sung by the children
all across the city.

419
00:24:48,800 --> 00:24:50,680
And the plaque. You did all those things?

420
00:24:50,680 --> 00:24:53,040
Yes! I was trying to rebuild his...

421
00:24:55,830 --> 00:24:58,880
