426
00:25:08,280 --> 00:25:09,760
Since Your Highness has helped me

427
00:25:10,160 --> 00:25:11,230
rebuilt my reputation,

428
00:25:11,680 --> 00:25:13,560
I'm sure Her Majesty will take pity on me as well.

429
00:25:13,590 --> 00:25:15,400
I shall not trouble Your Highness any further.

430
00:25:15,680 --> 00:25:16,880
What do you mean?

431
00:25:17,310 --> 00:25:19,000
Are you still trying to join the harem?

432
00:25:19,800 --> 00:25:23,880
I shall not disturb both of you any further.

433
00:25:24,310 --> 00:25:24,950
I'll take my leave.

434
00:25:25,070 --> 00:25:25,640
You...

435
00:25:29,160 --> 00:25:32,040
Tan Er, Eighth Brother may appear cold and stoic,

436
00:25:32,160 --> 00:25:33,520
but he is warm-hearted.

437
00:25:33,640 --> 00:25:35,160
Please do not stay angry at him.

438
00:25:36,680 --> 00:25:37,590
You must be thirsty.

439
00:25:37,760 --> 00:25:38,520
Have a cup of tea.

440
00:25:39,920 --> 00:25:40,710
Oh, right.

441
00:25:41,400 --> 00:25:43,950
I just remembered that I've got some
government affairs to do.

442
00:25:44,310 --> 00:25:47,400
Why don't we arrange for another
meeting on another day?

443
00:25:48,520 --> 00:25:51,000
All right. I won't keep you any longer

444
00:25:51,000 --> 00:25:52,470
if you are busy.

445
00:25:52,830 --> 00:25:53,640
Okay.

446
00:25:53,920 --> 00:25:54,590
I'll walk you out.

447
00:25:54,640 --> 00:25:57,230
Don't bother. I can show myself out.

448
00:26:23,280 --> 00:26:24,710
Trying to ditch me? No way.

449
00:26:25,040 --> 00:26:26,830
Hold it right there, Fourteenth.

450
00:26:28,880 --> 00:26:31,880
What did you give Jing Xin just now?

451
00:26:33,160 --> 00:26:34,430
Greetings, Your Highness.

452
00:26:35,350 --> 00:26:36,950
Do you still rank fourteenth?

453
00:26:38,000 --> 00:26:40,950
Still? I've always been the fourteenth son.

454
00:26:41,830 --> 00:26:42,800
That's odd.

455
00:26:43,830 --> 00:26:46,830
Men in Dongyue can only marry one woman.

456
00:26:47,040 --> 00:26:48,520
It takes time for a woman to carry a child...

457
00:26:48,920 --> 00:26:49,830
Does that mean

458
00:26:50,350 --> 00:26:52,000
that you are much younger than Mo Lian Cheng

459
00:26:52,000 --> 00:26:53,230
and Mo Yan Chen?

460
00:26:53,800 --> 00:26:55,710
Quite a few of my brothers are twins.

461
00:26:55,760 --> 00:26:58,070
Didn't you know, Your Highness?

462
00:26:59,470 --> 00:27:00,710
Twins?

463
00:27:00,880 --> 00:27:03,560
I learn something new again.

464
00:27:04,230 --> 00:27:05,830
Seem like they've tried very hard

465
00:27:06,070 --> 00:27:07,760
