466
00:27:09,760 --> 00:27:10,800
I've always wanted to ask this.

467
00:27:11,560 --> 00:27:13,590
Where are your other 13 brothers?

468
00:27:13,680 --> 00:27:15,520
Why have I never met them?

469
00:27:15,640 --> 00:27:17,040
I don't have 13 brothers.

470
00:27:17,040 --> 00:27:18,400
I have a sister.

471
00:27:18,760 --> 00:27:19,830
A sister?

472
00:27:21,000 --> 00:27:22,710
That's another person I don't know.

473
00:27:23,350 --> 00:27:25,710
Then do you have a brother named Mo Yi Huai?

474
00:27:26,070 --> 00:27:26,760
No.

475
00:27:28,560 --> 00:27:30,190
Oh, I remember now.

476
00:27:30,760 --> 00:27:32,040
Father once said that I had another brother

477
00:27:32,070 --> 00:27:33,230
before Eldest Brother was born.

478
00:27:33,520 --> 00:27:35,950
But they gave him to another family
the moment he was born.

479
00:27:36,120 --> 00:27:39,040
I think that was the name they gave him then.

480
00:27:39,430 --> 00:27:40,800
How did you know about this, Your Highness?

481
00:27:43,110 --> 00:27:44,190
(So that's why...)

482
00:27:45,230 --> 00:27:48,470
(Qu Tan Er and Mo Yan Chen were childhood playmates.)

483
00:27:49,110 --> 00:27:50,800
I... I have to go back now.

484
00:27:51,070 --> 00:27:52,310
Please excuse me, Your Highness.

485
00:27:58,860 --> 00:27:59,800
Jing Xin.

486
00:28:06,680 --> 00:28:08,920
When did the two of you get so close?

487
00:28:09,710 --> 00:28:12,190
Who? What do you mean, "close"?

488
00:28:12,190 --> 00:28:13,230
Still hiding it.

489
00:28:14,070 --> 00:28:15,310
You and Fourteenth, of course.

490
00:28:16,430 --> 00:28:17,560
Well, that's because

491
00:28:17,800 --> 00:28:20,230
