499
00:28:36,400 --> 00:28:38,310
(Why is she saying something like this now?)

500
00:28:38,560 --> 00:28:39,590
What are you thinking?

501
00:28:40,590 --> 00:28:41,560
Let's go home.

502
00:28:50,430 --> 00:28:52,520
Greetings, Your Majesty.

503
00:29:01,520 --> 00:29:02,230
Sit.

504
00:29:02,400 --> 00:29:03,880
Give me a shoulder massage.

505
00:29:19,310 --> 00:29:22,110
With Jing Xin guarding the palace gate
day and night,

506
00:29:22,280 --> 00:29:23,800
Mo Lian Cheng

507
00:29:24,110 --> 00:29:26,470
won't even have a chance to seduce others.

508
00:29:27,710 --> 00:29:30,160
If he dares to come, then I'll dare to ruin his plans.

509
00:29:32,280 --> 00:29:35,760
Want to be alone with her? Not a chance.

510
00:29:40,160 --> 00:29:40,830
Your Highness.

511
00:29:43,350 --> 00:29:45,110
What is it? Is something up?

512
00:29:45,230 --> 00:29:46,070
Your Highness,

513
00:29:46,190 --> 00:29:48,590
Eighth Young Master was reported
to have entered the palace.

514
00:29:48,920 --> 00:29:49,950
What?

515
00:29:50,800 --> 00:29:52,350
You can't go, Your Highness.

516
00:29:52,590 --> 00:29:55,350
What if Her Majesty and Eighth Young Master
are discussing something important?

517
00:29:56,470 --> 00:29:57,280
All right.

518
00:29:57,280 --> 00:29:58,830
You've been guarding the gate
all day. You must be tired.

519
00:29:58,880 --> 00:29:59,950
Go and get some rest.

520
00:30:00,520 --> 00:30:01,950
I'll see

521
00:30:02,070 --> 00:30:04,310
what they have to discuss
in the middle of the night!

522
00:30:04,880 --> 00:30:07,350
All right. You've worked hard.

523
00:30:10,800 --> 00:30:12,110
Her Highness

524
00:30:12,190 --> 00:30:14,310
