529
00:30:36,680 --> 00:30:38,520
Stop! Let go!

530
00:30:38,590 --> 00:30:39,920
How dare you be so rude to Her Majesty!

531
00:30:41,110 --> 00:30:43,590
It's all right. He just spilled some tea.

532
00:30:44,110 --> 00:30:45,590
Why are you here?

533
00:30:47,710 --> 00:30:50,280
It was just a misunderstanding.

534
00:31:01,800 --> 00:31:05,310
Cheng Cheng, why are you here?

535
00:31:05,710 --> 00:31:07,280
It was just a misunderstanding.

536
00:31:07,400 --> 00:31:08,470
What's wrong with him?

537
00:31:08,520 --> 00:31:09,710
Should we ask for an imperial physician?

538
00:31:19,070 --> 00:31:21,230
No need. I was just taken aback for a moment.

539
00:31:21,430 --> 00:31:22,430
I apologize for scaring Your Majesty.

540
00:31:24,880 --> 00:31:27,350
Why did you come here at this hour, Tan Er?

541
00:31:29,640 --> 00:31:31,800
I've been having trouble sleeping recently.

